Package: amplicon
Type: Package
Title: Statistics and visualization for amplicon data
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2019-4-8
Author: Yong-Xin Liu
Maintainer: Yong-Xin Liu <metagenome@126.com>
Description: A basic statistics and plotting pipeline for amplicon data.
    1. Alpha boxplot with LSD.test / anova;
    2. Alpha rarefraction curve in samples and groups with standard error;
    3. PCoA plot with confidence ellipse and Adonis p-value;
    4. Constrained PCoA / CCA with variant, p-value and confidence ellipse;
    5. Taxonomy stackplot in group and sample.
    0.1.1 add beta_cpcoa_dis.R support constrained distance matrix
